    "Safety improvements peak at 20% sparsity, similar to our findings with the previously introduced malicious task dataset.",
    "We focus on Llama2 throughout this section.",
    "We inspect attention patterns and qualitatively observe that pruned models have sharper attention.",
    "Vig and Belinkov (2019) found that the entropy of attention patterns correlates with high-level semantic behavior: across various model depths, both the entropy of the attention patterns and their role in understanding sequence semantics evolve.",
